sp.r.s.tvaa tu gaava.h "samayanti paapa.m datvaa tu gaavastridiva.m nayanti|
sa.mrak.sitaa"scopanayanti vitta.m gobhirnna tulya.m dhanama sti ki~ncit|| 102||
sampannama"snaati dadaati nitya.m paapaapaha.m mitravivarddhana.m ca|
sa eva caartha.h paribhujyate ca gobhirnna tulya.m dhanamasti ki~ncit|| 103||
